      "content": "but there isn't any relief. doctors just keep giving me more pills and more things that don't work. it's just a cycle of misery. sometimes i look at people just living their lives and it feels so unfair. honestly, sometimes i think the only way to truly stop the pain is to just... not be here anymore. it feels like the only kind of peace that's actually possible.",
